title: Ebro In The Morning - Black ISH Wednesday + Musiq Soulchild Vs. Anthony Hamilton
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 2/16/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez, and the crew are in the studio talking about the Musiq Soulchild Vs. Anthony Hamilton VERZUZ (1), Drill music and Eric Adams (26), and we play a little bit of Black ISH Wednesday(50). Get excited for the gurus to help solve your problems, to learn some Black Facts, and to find out when Kendrick is playing new music. All that and more on Ebro In The Morning! 

Click here to learn about the Hot 97 - Securing the Future initiative.
